<br />
<br />I'd need to think about line-drawing for a while. But this really makes me want to have some cheesy "CG" movie in my game. But I see what you're saying about keeping a copy of the name table in RAM. It's a pretty simple idea, it's just that it might take forever to actually draw the lines</div>

